title: Cryptovoxels parcel acquisition
body:
There is a new parcel release in the Vibe island of cryptovoxels. The reserve price seems to be 1 ETH for those parcels. Given each parcels area and maximum building height, I believe that we can bid up to 2ETH for the bigger parcels. Links here:  
https://opensea.io/assets/cryptovoxels?search[numericTraits][0][name]=height&search[numericTraits][0][ranges][0][max]=48&search[numericTraits][0][ranges][0][min]=12.7&search[numericTraits][1][name]=area&search[numericTraits][1][ranges][0][min]=160&search[numericTraits][1][ranges][0][max]=495&search[stringTraits][0][name]=suburb&search[stringTraits][0][values][0]=West%20End

https://opensea.io/assets/cryptovoxels?search[numericTraits][0][name]=area&search[numericTraits][0][ranges][0][max]=495&search[numericTraits][0][ranges][0][min]=141&search[numericTraits][1][name]=height&search[numericTraits][1][ranges][0][min]=11.3&search[numericTraits][1][ranges][0][max]=48&search[resultModel]=ASSETS&search[stringTraits][0][name]=island&search[stringTraits][0][values][0]=Vibes

The cheapest parcel in with the same feature for sale is available for 2.89ETH on San Fransisco. (152m² and 14m build height)
https://opensea.io/assets/0x79986af15539de2db9a5086382daeda917a9cf0c/4652

There is an option to be teleported in different parcel in your building, so we could use this parcel along with other parcels in the future.
example: https://www.cryptovoxels.com/parcels/4650

There is a feature for exclusive events in cryptovoxels as Etheopath stated here: 
https://discordapp.com/channels/816864150016753705/826530893782581309/842803279184527406

Here is Beeple's B.20 monument (quite big parcel): 
https://www.cryptovoxels.com/parcels/1226
choices: Yes, Place a bid up to 1.5ETH
Yes, Place a bid up to 2ETH
No, we will find a better deal
